item.title: Pipeline processing 2
item.description: Welcome to pipeline processing part 2. I feel I need to backtrack slightly from the previous post, having worked with pipelines for quite some time I have the advantage of knowing all of the details that may be alluded to in these articles without being effected by any omissions I may make, obviously you guys aren’t in that position, so I’m going to try and rectify that a bit now.
